1. *Pripremi* voće za doručak. (Prepare the fruit for breakfast.)

2. Ona je *pripremila* obrok za put. (She prepared the meal for the journey.)

3. On će *pripremiti* sve što je potrebno. (He will prepare everything that is needed.)

4. *Pripremili* smo sve za večeru. (We prepared everything for dinner.)

5. Oni su *pripremali* sastojke za salatu. (They were preparing the ingredients for the salad.)